media:group.media:title: Jerma Streams with Chat - HITMAN 3 (Part 4)
media:group.media:description:
Watch Jerma985's live streams at https://www.twitch.tv/jerma985.

This video covers chapter 1 of 2 of a multi-chapter stream.
Next Chapter: https://youtu.be/NOuB5nt81DA (Multiversus, Part 3)
